o:TemplateTargetItem.a:Name: mdde_Entity_TTView_Template
o:TemplateTargetItem.a:TemplateTargetItem.Value:
.vbscript(%Stereotype%, %Code%) Dim strStereotype : strStereotype = ScriptInputArray(0) Dim strCode : strCode = ScriptInputArray(1)
ScriptResult = ""
' If the stereotype contains "with TT view" it will return the TT view name. If (InStr(strStereotype,"with TT view") > 0) Then ScriptResult = Trim(Mid(strCode,1,7) & "TT_" & Mid(strCode,8,247)) End If .endvbscript
